{"tid":2069363,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"逾億元豪宅曝光 關之琳屋企歎茶欣賞雙彩虹","createTime":"2020-06-18T10:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T10:54:49.000Z","uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"17a6653a37d618a952e79249626cca8168272341","tid":2069363,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:20:35.000Z","msg":"昨日香港有多區看到雙彩虹，當時身在半山豪宅的關之琳（之之）也欣賞到此美景，她拍下照片於社交平台分享，留言「What a lucky sign for HK#doublerainbow」，好友陳栢熹（Harris）留言「想你！樓下的住戶敬上」，原來兩人是樓上樓下的鄰居。其後，楊小娟在其社交帳號甫出之之在家中一邊歎茶、一邊看美景的照片，並留言：「最美的姐在家裏與最美的彩虹相遇！」相中看到之之市值約1.5億元的豪宅，可以眺望維多利亞港美景，視覺上絕對是一大享受。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20200617/s00009/9c81aacbdfa11059aa3248fc02e23607.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20200617%2Fs00009%2F9c81aacbdfa11059aa3248fc02e23607.jpg&h=ed8d880e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這些機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1334452bb334bd3a8deebe0df99641f9d1e6fbe3","tid":2069363,"uid":77959,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:25:45.000Z","msg":"咁唔係個個都肯玩高爾夫球嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f7d0b1e1809f01b3fe39c252e0e43e1b84b82c","tid":2069363,"uid":24339,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1334452bb334bd3a8deebe0df99641f9d1e6fbe3","tid":2069363,"uid":77959,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:25:45.000Z","msg":"咁唔係個個都肯玩高爾夫球嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"唔知你肯唔肯<br />\n我就肯"},{"pid":"e82c923460091f14cacc905a940762febbe21ab4","tid":2069363,"uid":77959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c6f7d0b1e1809f01b3fe39c252e0e43e1b84b82c","tid":2069363,"uid":24339,"like":2,"dislike":2,"